<h2 data-heading="查看端口" dir="auto">查看端口</h2>
<p dir="auto"><span alt="Pasted image 20250410152949.png" src="Pasted image 20250410152949.png" class="internal-embed media-embed image-embed is-loaded"><img alt="Pasted image 20250410152949.png" src="data:image/png;base64,"></span><br>

<pre><code>netstat -an | grep "LISTEN"
</code></pre>
<p dir="auto"><span alt="Pasted image 20250616081647.png" src="Pasted image 20250616081647.png" class="internal-embed media-embed image-embed is-loaded"><img alt="Pasted image 20250616081647.png" src="data:image/png;base64,"></span></p>
